! Types (standard numbered (1-99) and named)
! filter based on the source address only
! use as packet filters by which you can filter traffic coimg from one network to another.
! Standard IP ACLs should be placed as close to the destination of traffic as possible.
! inboud or outbound directons.
! all traffic is denied except for what i explicity permit.
Router(config)#access-list {1-99 | 1300-1999} { permit | deny } <source-addres> <wildcard-mask>
#ip access-group { number | name } {in|out}
















